column2: There are alot of actresses able to take the role of Mera in AM2, however i would prefer to see Emillia due to the fact that good chemistry between actors make for a better movie. Hope she gets the role IF Amber is to be replaced <3
column26: DC Entertainment: Emilia Clarke Become Mera To Replace Amber Heard In ‘Aquaman 2’
column33: Warner Brothers: DC Entertainment: Emilia Clarke Become Mera To Replace Amber Heard In ‘Aquaman 2’
column34:
Do you think Amber Heard should be replaced by Emilia Clarke in Aquaman 2? Would you car to see Emilia Clarke as Mera? How should the Aquaman follow-up handle a replacement? Share your thoguhts in thec omments!

Digital artist BossLogic took the idea and ran with it. In his latest concept, BossLogic reveals what Emilia Clarke could look like as Mera for Aquaman 2. It’s hard to deny that the former Game of Thrones star looks the part, as the new outfit the artist puts her in immediately gives her a regal look. Clarke’s acting talents would definitely be a big step up for the DCEU and Game of Thrones fans would be wholly excited to see the British star reunite with Jason Momoa. You can see Emilia Clarke as Amber Heard’s Mera replacement in the concept design below.

Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. The actor has already lost the role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Animals 3 and also Disney has commented that they will not have him for a new Pirates of the Caribbean movie. While the actress could lose her job as Mera in Aquaman 2 and there are people who ask for Emilia Clarke to replace her.

column2:
Dear Amber,
I am a domestic abuse survivor.
You will not minimise our experiences and our fight to become survivors by claiming you speak for us.
You do not speak for me. You speak exactly as my abuser did. Shame on you. 
Signed

column34:
Do you think Amber Heard should be replaced by Emilia Clarke in Aquaman 2? Would you car to see Emilia Clarke as Mera? How should the Aquaman follow-up handle a replacement? Share your thoguhts in thec omments!

Digital artist BossLogic took the idea and ran with it. In his latest concept, BossLogic reveals what Emilia Clarke could look like as Mera for Aquaman 2. It’s hard to deny that the former Game of Thrones star looks the part, as the new outfit the artist puts her in immediately gives her a regal look. Clarke’s acting talents would definitely be a big step up for the DCEU and Game of Thrones fans would be wholly excited to see the British star reunite with Jason Momoa. You can see Emilia Clarke as Amber Heard’s Mera replacement in the concept design below.

Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. The actor has already lost the role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Animals 3 and also Disney has commented that they will not have him for a new Pirates of the Caribbean movie. While the actress could lose her job as Mera in Aquaman 2 and there are people who ask for Emilia Clarke to replace her.

Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. While the actress could lose her job as Mera in Aquaman 2 and there are people who ask for Emilia Clarke to replace her.

Do you think Amber Heard should be replaced by Emilia Clarke in Aquaman 2? Would you car to see Emilia Clarke as Mera? How should the Aquaman follow-up handle a replacement? Share your thoguhts in thec omments!

Digital artist BossLogic took the idea and ran with it. In his latest concept, BossLogic reveals what Emilia Clarke could look like as Mera for Aquaman 2. It’s hard to deny that the former Game of Thrones star looks the part, as the new outfit the artist puts her in immediately gives her a regal look. Clarke’s acting talents would definitely be a big step up for the DCEU and Game of Thrones fans would be wholly excited to see the British star reunite with Jason Momoa. Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. column2:
I will not support a self-confessed, yet unrepentant, abuser of at least two of her domestic partners. 
I’m signing because I’ve heard the tapes Ms Heard made in which she admits repeatedly hitting Mr. Depp, states she can’t promise not to again, clearly gaslights Mr. Depp, and engages in further violent & disgusting behaviors typical of some Cluster B personality disordered people- particularly Malignant Narcissism. In the tapes Mr. Depp can be heard endeavoring to navigate kindly in an impossible situation with someone behaving like a toxic malignant narcissist- classic conversation between abuser (Heard) & victim (Depp). Heard also has a verifiable legal history as a domestic abuser, which points to repetition compulsion.
Mr. Depp has surely lost too much already, let’s not continue to victimize and penalize him for the simple “crime” of falling for a girlmonster. Conversely let’s not reward Ms. Heard for her terrible behavior.
Both parties need help- Ms. Heard for Cognitive Behavioural Therapy; and Mr Depp needs trauma counseling, to heal his possible attachment disorder, & heal with holistic health therapies, along with Adeno B12 and top notch Genomic B-complex therapy. Both parties need to heal. And the world at large should Not be further abused by having to view films by, or be further gaslighted by, Heard.

column33: Warner Brothers: DC Entertainment: Emilia Clarke Become Mera To Replace Amber Heard In ‘Aquaman 2’
column34:
Do you think Amber Heard should be replaced by Emilia Clarke in Aquaman 2? Would you car to see Emilia Clarke as Mera? How should the Aquaman follow-up handle a replacement? Share your thoguhts in thec omments!

Digital artist BossLogic took the idea and ran with it. In his latest concept, BossLogic reveals what Emilia Clarke could look like as Mera for Aquaman 2. It’s hard to deny that the former Game of Thrones star looks the part, as the new outfit the artist puts her in immediately gives her a regal look. Clarke’s acting talents would definitely be a big step up for the DCEU and Game of Thrones fans would be wholly excited to see the British star reunite with Jason Momoa. You can see Emilia Clarke as Amber Heard’s Mera replacement in the concept design below.

Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. The actor has already lost the role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Animals 3 and also Disney has commented that they will not have him for a new Pirates of the Caribbean movie. While the actress could lose her job as Mera in Aquaman 2 and there are people who ask for Emilia Clarke to replace her.

Digital artist BossLogic took the idea and ran with it. In his latest concept, BossLogic reveals what Emilia Clarke could look like as Mera for Aquaman 2. It’s hard to deny that the former Game of Thrones star looks the part, as the new outfit the artist puts her in immediately gives her a regal look. Clarke’s acting talents would definitely be a big step up for the DCEU and Game of Thrones fans would be wholly excited to see the British star reunite with Jason Momoa. You can see Emilia Clarke as Amber Heard’s Mera replacement in the concept design below.

Both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are involved in a great controversy over their judicial confrontations. The actor has already lost the role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Animals 3 and also Disney has commented that they will not have him for a new Pirates of the Caribbean movie. While the actress could lose her job as Mera in Aquaman 2 and there are people who ask for Emilia Clarke to replace her.
